    <p class="measure f4 f3-ns lh-copy">
      When floats are used for layouts - they need a clearfix solution. This
      helps prevent layout problems caused by the elements being removed from
      the block context of the surrounding elements.
    </p>
  </article>
  <div class="ph3 ph5-ns pt4 pb5">
